{
  "version": "0.9.5",
  "changelog": [
    "### Added",
    "**Patcher version tracking** \u2014 After a successful patch, the patcher writes the manifest version to `Macros/coopui_installed_version.txt` so support can see what version players have. Patcher UI shows \"Installed: X \u00b7 Available: Y\" when updates are available and \"Up to date (vX)\" when current. ItemUI startup message uses this file when present so patcher users see the same version in-game."
  ],
